text:
If this doesnt bust imposter syndrome, I dont know what will:
<https://twitter.com/jensimmons/status/1445377175851503618?s=20>
If you don’t know Jen Simmons, highly encourage following her stuff. Shes influenced a lot of the most important HTML CSS and browser improvements over the last 10+ years.

I’ll share a similar one. I’ve worked on the HubSpot CMS for several years and grew my career around it. HubL is HubSpot’s special fork of JinJava, a port of Jinja to Java.

*I dont know Java.*

It’s okay not to know everything. The best people know - that they dont know, and actively seek to surround themselves with those who do. Strive to put yourself in situations where you wont be the smartest person in the room and listen to those who are.
